description: The MSCI Emerging Markets Low Carbon SRI Selection Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies across various Emerging Markets countries with high ESG characteristics and low carbon exposures excluding companies involved in tobacco-related products, relative to their peers Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI Emerging Markets ESG UCITS ETF 1C
